{"tid":1624562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"郵政服務特別安排","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:14:44.000Z","uid":34420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7089387aa890f83435125d4944688a34550ad106","tid":1624562,"uid":34420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:14:44.000Z","msg":"香港郵政今日（十月五日）公布， 所有郵政局及郵政信箱大堂將於今日下午一時關閉。郵政總局（包括郵政信箱大堂）和機場郵政局將於十月六日及十月七日（重陽節假期）休息。<br />\n<br />\n　　顧客欲知進一步詳情，請瀏覽香港郵政網頁（<a href=\"http://www.hongkongpost.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongpost.hk&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=a10b7f5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hongkongpost.hk</a>），或致電香港郵政查詢熱線2921 2222。   <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年10月5日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間11時47分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/05/P2019100500453.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201910%2F05%2FP2019100500453.htm&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=da619d9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/05/P2019100500453.htm</a>"}]}